{"tid":993134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"植物人遭性侵產子　驗DNA逮到療養院男護士","createTime":"2019-01-23T16:30:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-24T09:34:37.000Z","uid":72009,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ca39e4ab4bfdb1085c6401b561f2068f88bda0aa","tid":993134,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T16:30:36.000Z","msg":"鳳凰城警察局長威廉斯（Jeri Williams）表示，警方以性侵和虐待弱勢成人罪逮捕持有護士執照的薩瑟蘭（Nathan Sutherland）。威廉斯指出，薩瑟蘭在哈辛達療養院工作，並負責照護受害的女病患。警方發言人湯普森（Tommy Thompson）說，經DNA測試後，確認性侵女病患的人就是薩瑟蘭。<br />\n美聯社報導，這名29歲的女病患3歲時喪失行為能力，她在去年12月29日產下一名男嬰。療養院員工聲稱不知道女病患懷孕，根據法院文件記錄，她最後一次接受身體檢查是去年4月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190124/1506245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190124%2F1506245&d=abUks92o3xd5TFNNtPNxLtibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=de57e933\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20190124%2F1506245&h=937b30e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20190124/1506245</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該不止一個中出，不過佢Ｄ精強Ｄ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea2847b85d797054f197e0ab8496367d63975f7","tid":993134,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"仲唔走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f827845f198c83aca30cadc1b1e4a0648300cbd","tid":993134,"uid":9286,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6ea2847b85d797054f197e0ab8496367d63975f7","tid":993134,"uid":121546,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:05:27.000Z","msg":"仲唔走佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"好似六合彩咁 開結果先知邊個<br />\n走佬仲大獲啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f90fcb4abda